    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>https://hwiberg.github.io/authors/admin/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://hwiberg.github.io/authors/admin/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello! I am a fourth year PhD candidate at the Operations Research Center at MIT, working with &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mit.edu/~dbertsim/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Professor Dimitris Bertsimas&lt;/a&gt;. My research leverages optimization and machine learning techniques in healthcare. I am working to develop novel approaches to improve patient care based on individual characteristics, including medical history and genomic data. I am particularly interested in the interpretability of machine learning models and applications to oncology. I previously worked at &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.athenahealth.com/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;athenahealth&lt;/a&gt;, a healthcare IT company, on their Data Science team.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
